  "description": "First passive live-shadow canary contract. Manual, local, opt-in, record-only, no effects. The canary consumes only already-redacted local canary packets and writes only local evidence records. It does not read live traffic, persist raw input, start a daemon/watcher, integrate runtime/adapters, execute tools, write memory/config, publish externally, approve, block, allow, authorize, delete, schedule retention/deletion, or enforce.",
